WEBVTT

28:34.734 --> 28:35.817
That is the first murder.

28:36.025 --> 28:37.442
The other seven murders followed it.

28:38.150 --> 28:39.984
Already in shock?

28:40.817 --> 28:42.609
Actually, you can't term it as a murder.

28:43.192 --> 28:45.192
It's a treatment I discovered
to cure my problem.

28:46.859 --> 28:47.775
What problem?

28:50.567 --> 28:51.942
Tourette syndrome.

28:52.525 --> 28:54.692
It tortured me a lot
during my childhood.

28:56.067 --> 28:58.150
Now I am torturing others for this.

29:02.567 --> 29:04.484
After sleeping with a
husband that she hated;
